# It seems we do not have any Iron Ore available in our inventory, which means we cannot smelt any more Iron Plates at this time. 
# Since we need at least 1 more Iron Plate to craft the Iron Gear Wheels, we will have to gather more Iron Ore.

# Step 90: Locate the nearest Iron Ore resource patch to gather more Iron Ore
iron_ore_position = nearest(Resource.IronOre)
move_to(iron_ore_position)

# Step 91: Harvest Iron Ore from the patch (let's collect at least 10 units to ensure we have enough)
harvest_resource(position=iron_ore_position, quantity=10)

# Step 92: Check the inventory after harvesting Iron Ore
print(f'Inventory after harvesting Iron Ore: {inspect_inventory()}')
